OL,3,CNew Caledonia: Where is the French
OL,4,Coverseas territory 'heading for civil
OL,5,Cwar'?
OL,7,FThe violence in New Caledonia has led
OL,8,Fto fresh discussion of France's
OL,9,Fcolonial past, raising new questions
OL,10,Fabout Mr Macron's handling of that
OL,11,Flegacy.
OL,13,FWhere is New Caledonia?
OL,15,FNew Caledonia is a group of islands in
OL,16,Fthe , lying between Australia and New
OL,17,FZealand, with a population of 270,000
OL,18,Fpeople.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/15
