OL,3,CNew Caledonia: Where is the French
OL,4,Coverseas territory 'heading for civil
OL,5,Cwar'?
OL,7,FIt has been a French colony since the
OL,8,Fmid-1800s, and became a French
OL,9,Foverseas territory in 1946.
OL,11,FThe islands have experienced decades
OL,12,Fof tension between the indigenous
OL,13,FKanaks - who have long sought
OL,14,Findependence - and the descendants of
OL,15,FFrench colonisers, who wish New
OL,16,FCaledonia to remain a part of France.
OL,18,FPerhaps most demonstrative of this was
OL,19,Fa period of violent uprisings in the
OL,20,F1980s, known as "the events", in which
OL,21,Fdozens of people died.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/15
