OL,3,CNew Caledonia: Where is the French
OL,4,Coverseas territory 'heading for civil
OL,5,Cwar'?
OL,7,FIt was the biggest threat to French
OL,8,Frule in the islands' history, quelled
OL,9,Fby a series of agreements outlining a
OL,10,Fpath to gradual autonomy for the
OL,11,FKanaks.
OL,13,FBut it wasn't until 2018 that the
OL,14,Ffirst independence referendum was held
OL,15,Fon the islands. Three referendums have
OL,16,Fnow been held, with the anti-
OL,17,Findependence side winning out each
OL,18,Ftime.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/15
