OL,7,FStill, pro-independence leaders have
OL,8,Fcalled for another vote, arguing that
OL,9,Fthe third referendum should have been
OL,10,Fdelayed.
OL,12,FMany Kanaks were prohibited from
OL,13,Fvoting in the 2021 vote by mourning
OL,14,Fcustoms, following a coronavirus
OL,15,Foutbreak that devastated communities
OL,16,Fthere.
OL,18,FWhy is it important to France?
