OL,7,FThe calculus in France has changed in
OL,8,Frecent years, as the south-pacific
OL,9,Fregion takes up a more .
OL,11,Ffor influence in the region
OL,12,Fintensifies, French officials fear
OL,13,Fthat China could gain sway in an
OL,14,Findependent New Caledonia - just as it
OL,15,Fhas sought to do in the Solomon
OL,16,FIslands.
OL,18,FNew Caledonia is also one of the
OL,19,Fworld's biggest nickel producers,
OL,20,Fholding between 20-30% of the world's
OL,21,Freserves.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/15
