OL,3,CNew Caledonia: Where is the French
OL,4,Coverseas territory 'heading for civil
OL,5,Cwar'?
OL,7,FPresident Macron visited the islands
OL,8,Flast July to emphasise his vision for
OL,9,Fthe French-Pacific outpost.
OL,11,F"New Caledonia is French because it
OL,12,Fhas chosen to remain French," Mr
OL,13,FMacron told the crowd. "No going back.
OL,14,FNo stuttering."
OL,16,FWhat has sparked the recent violence?
OL,18,FThe latest period of unrest erupted on
OL,19,FMay 13, when French lawmakers in Paris
OL,20,Fdebated making changes to New
OL,21,FCaledonian voting lists.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/15
