OL,7,FThe French National Assembly approved
OL,8,Fa bill that would, among other
OL,9,Fchanges, allow residents who have
OL,10,Flived in New Caledonia for 10 years or
OL,11,Fmore to cast ballots in provincial
OL,12,Felections.
OL,14,FOpponents say the measure will benefit
OL,15,Fpro-France politicians, and further
OL,16,Fmarginalise the Kanaks by
