OL,7,FUnder prior accords, voting in
OL,8,Fprovincial elections was restricted to
OL,9,Fthose who had resided in New Caledonia
OL,10,Fsince before 1998, and their
OL,11,Fdescendants.
OL,13,FThe measure was aimed at giving
OL,14,Fgreater representation to the Kanaks
OL,15,Fwho had, at that point, become a
OL,16,Fminority group on the islands.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/15
