OL,3,CNew Caledonia: Where is the French
OL,4,Coverseas territory 'heading for civil
OL,5,Cwar'?
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, Paris declared a 12-day
OL,8,Fminimum state of emergency on the
OL,9,Fislands, and rushed in over 1,000
OL,10,Freinforcements to bolster security
OL,11,Fforces that had lost control of parts
OL,12,Fof the capital, Noumea.
OL,14,FAt least six people have been killed,
OL,15,Fincluding two police officers.
OL,17,FParts of the city have become no-go
OL,18,Fzones, with buildings torched, shops
OL,19,Fpillages, and makeshift barricades set
OL,20,Fup.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/15
