OL,7,F"The protests reveal the determination
OL,8,Fof our young people to no longer let
OL,9,FFrance rule them," said Daniel Goa,
OL,10,Fthe president of the pro-independence
OL,11,FCaledonian Union party, although he
OL,12,Fcalled for a stop to the violence.
OL,14,FWhat happens next?
OL,16,FWith police given emergency powers and
OL,17,Fa 6pm to 6am curfew in effect, French
OL,18,Fauthorities say security forces are
OL,19,Fstarting to contain the unrest.
