OL,7,FA priority for French authorities has
OL,8,Fbeen clearing the highway to the
OL,9,Finternational airport, in order to
OL,10,Fallow stranded tourists to leave.
OL,12,FAustralia and New Zealand sent planes
OL,13,Fto New Caledonia on Tuesday to begin
OL,14,Fbringing citizens home. Some 300
OL,15,FAustralians and 50 New Zealanders are
OL,16,Fcurrently stranded
