OL,7,FPresident Macron's visit will aim to
OL,8,Fsubdue tensions. He will travel to the
OL,9,Fislands on Tuesday evening, but no
OL,10,Fdetails have been given regarding the
OL,11,Flength of his stay.
OL,13,F"Faced with the outbreak of violence,
OL,14,Fthe priority is the return of order to
OL,15,Fallow dialogue to resume," said a
OL,16,FFrench government spokesperson.
OL,18,F"We are clear: much remains to be done
OL,19,Fbefore the return to normal. The
OL,20,Fgovernment is fully mobilised."
