OL,7,FLocal authorities have also called for
OL,8,Fcalm, with the High Commissioner of
OL,9,Fthe Republic, Louis Le Franc, warning
OL,10,Fthe territory is "heading straight for
OL,11,Fa civil war".
OL,13,FFrench said re-establishing order was
OL,14,Fnecessary for further dialogue to
OL,15,Fbegin.
OL,17,FBut pro-independence parties say they
OL,18,Fwant the French government to withdraw
OL,19,Fthe reforms before they restart talks.
